(26, 'ХК  Авангард (Омск)', '<p style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">«Авангард»</span>&nbsp;— советский и&nbsp;<a href=\"https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%A0%D0%BE%D1%81%D1%81%D0%B8%D1%8F\" title=\"Россия\" style=\"color: rgb(6, 69, 173); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">российский</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%A5%D0%BE%D0%BA%D0%BA%D0%B5%D0%B9%D0%BD%D1%8B%D0%B9_%D0%BA%D0%BB%D1%83%D0%B1\" title=\"Хоккейный клуб\" style=\"color: rgb(6, 69, 173); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">хоккейный клуб</a>&nbsp;из города&nbsp;<a href=\"https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%9E%D0%BC%D1%81%D0%BA\" title=\"Омск\" style=\"color: rgb(6, 69, 173); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Омска</a>, выступающий в&nbsp;<a href=\"https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%9A%D0%BE%D0%BD%D1%82%D0%B8%D0%BD%D0%B5%D0%BD%D1%82%D0%B0%D0%BB%D1%8C%D0%BD%D0%B0%D1%8F_%D1%85%D0%BE%D0%BA%D0%BA%D0%B5%D0%B9%D0%BD%D0%B0%D1%8F_%D0%BB%D0%B8%D0%B3%D0%B0\" title=\"Континентальная хоккейная лига\" style=\"color: rgb(6, 69, 173); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">КХЛ</a>. Чемпион РСФСР&nbsp;<a href=\"https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%A7%D0%B5%D0%BC%D0%BF%D0%B8%D0%BE%D0%BD%D0%B0%D1%82_%D0%A0%D0%A1%D0%A4%D0%A1%D0%A0_%D0%BF%D0%BE_%D1%85%D0%BE%D0%BA%D0%BA%D0%B5%D1%8E_%D1%81_%D1%88%D0%B0%D0%B9%D0%B1%D0%BE%D0%B9_1958/1959\" title=\"Чемпионат РСФСР по хоккею с шайбой 1958/1959\" style=\"color: rgb(6, 69, 173); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">1959</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%A7%D0%B5%D0%BC%D0%BF%D0%B8%D0%BE%D0%BD%D0%B0%D1%82_%D0%A0%D0%A1%D0%A4%D0%A1%D0%A0_%D0%BF%D0%BE_%D1%85%D0%BE%D0%BA%D0%BA%D0%B5%D1%8E_%D1%81_%D1%88%D0%B0%D0%B9%D0%B1%D0%BE%D0%B9_1972/1973\" title=\"Чемпионат РСФСР по хоккею с шайбой 1972/1973\" style=\"color: rgb(6, 69, 173); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">1973</a>&nbsp;и чемпион России&nbsp;<a href=\"https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%A7%D0%B5%D0%BC%D0%BF%D0%B8%D0%BE%D0%BD%D0%B0%D1%82_%D0%A0%D0%BE%D1%81%D1%81%D0%B8%D0%B8_%D0%BF%D0%BE_%D1%85%D0%BE%D0%BA%D0%BA%D0%B5%D1%8E_%D1%81_%D1%88%D0%B0%D0%B9%D0%B1%D0%BE%D0%B9_2003/2004\" title=\"Чемпионат России по хоккею с шайбой 2003/2004\" style=\"color: rgb(6, 69, 173); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">2004</a>&nbsp;и&nbsp;<a href=\"https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%9A%D0%A5%D0%9B_%D0%B2_%D1%81%D0%B5%D0%B7%D0%BE%D0%BD%D0%B5_2020/2021\" title=\"КХЛ в сезоне 2020/2021\" style=\"color: rgb(6, 69, 173); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">2021</a>&nbsp;годов. Обладатель&nbsp;<a href=\"https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%9A%D1%83%D0%B1%D0%BE%D0%BA_%D0%93%D0%B0%D0%B3%D0%B0%D1%80%D0%B8%D0%BD%D0%B0\" title=\"Кубок Гагарина\" style=\"color: rgb(6, 69, 173); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Кубка Гагарина</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%A4%D0%B8%D0%BD%D0%B0%D0%BB_%D0%9A%D1%83%D0%B1%D0%BA%D0%B0_%D0%93%D0%B0%D0%B3%D0%B0%D1%80%D0%B8%D0%BD%D0%B0_2021\" title=\"Финал Кубка Гагарина 2021\" style=\"color: rgb(6, 69, 173); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">2021</a>&nbsp;года.</p><p style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Клуб основан 7 ноября 1950 года. Выступал под названиями «Спартак» (1950—1962), «Аэрофлот» (1962—1967), «Каучук» (1967—1972), «Химик» (1972—1974), «Шинник» (1974—1981). С 1981 года называется «Авангард». Выступает в КХЛ с момента основания лиги.</p>', 11, 'images/NYr03bAV942SX0Fob3WumqXgUwLyqXTGOkOc8oy0.png', 'images/UaNnlmTido2b8Vfz8r6Nd7ozOJMoLpywA6XxiHvk.jpg', '2023-03-27 14:40:42', '2023-03-27 14:40:42', NULL),
